Use the standard library
This is how to digitSum of s:
  Remember that total is 0
  Do this s's length times:
    Remember that ch is item total in s
    When ch is at least 48, then:
      When ch is at most 57, then:
        Increase total by diff of ch and 48
      End when
    End when
    Increase total
  End do
  The answer is total
